---
title  : Redline
summary: Lifecycle-oriented build tool
contact: Trans <transfire@gmail.com>

description:
  Redline is an advanced lifecycle-oriented build system.
  With Redline build tasks are user define service instances
  tied to stops along a line, or track. Whenever the redline
  console command is run a track is followed from beginning
  to designated destination.

requires:
- redtools
- facets
- pom
- qed (test)

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/redline
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/redline
  mail: http://groups.google.com/rubyworks-mailinglist

repositories:
  public: http://github.com/proutils/redline.git

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer

